### GET toate task-urile
GET http://localhost:5271/api/Tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### GET task după ID
GET http://localhost:5271/api/Tasks/1
Accept: application/json

###

### POST - adaugă un task nou
POST http://localhost:5271/api/Tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Scrie raportul",
  "description": "Raportul lunar",
  "isCompleted": false,
  "createdAt": "2025-11-24T18:30:00",
  "userEmail": "alina@example.com"
}

###

### PUT - actualizează task-ul cu ID = 1
PUT http://localhost:5271/api/Tasks/6
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 6,
  "title": "Scrie raportul revizuit",
  "description": "Raportul lunar actualizat",
  "isCompleted": true,
  "createdAt": "2025-11-24T19:00:00",
  "userEmail": "alina@example.com"
}

###

### DELETE - șterge task-ul cu ID = 1
DELETE http://localhost:5271/api/Tasks/1
